{"tid":1436546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] [緊急] 要有whatsapp宣傳戰線！！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:06:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T11:40:05.000Z","uid":229553,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc79ac4e0fc2b83e08d41aaf40eaaf270171ab5","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:06:58.000Z","msg":"成日收到or睇到好多fake news 訊息<br />\n保皇黨個邊成日出似是疑非既野去同鄉會既whatsapp group之類，再引大家轉載<br />\n例如：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">示威者打算搶劫提款中的市民<br />\n示威者出左手風炮可打爆道路、<br />\n一出現示威現場就會被控暴動罪、<br />\n示威者其實係廢青loser所以上街發洩不滿</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢堆假野真係睇到極火滾</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟提議，希望有個「Ｗhatsapp宣傳戰線」<br />\n定期發放真新聞同埋揭露正苦既奸計<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">例如：你知道嗎？林鄭打算用經濟要挾香港市民停止反抗！令我們甘願為奴！<br />\n例如：請廣傳！示威者警察無故向民居放催淚彈，引孕婦不適！廣傳朋友讓大家看見警察濫權真面目<br />\n例如：你知道嗎？警察總共發射1800枚催淚彈，當中更有過期生化武器，當香港人為實驗白老鼠！極度可惡，廣傳朋友抵制警方暴力！好人一生平安！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實呢樣野有時大家偶然都會收到，但唔夠定期同埋文本唔夠，搞到威力大減，而且要呢堆中老一輩share去群度就威力大增！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">「Ｗhatsapp宣傳戰線」<br />\n步驟1：開個google doc比大家upload自己家中長輩,同鄉會,藍絲,公司老一輩,中立,淺黃之類既電話號碼，務求有大量號碼<br />\n步驟2：用whatsapp批量send訊息軟件統計<br />\n步驟3：然後由戰線人員定期發放訊息</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">文宣新方向！whatsapp戰線！大家唔好忽視！</span></span><br />\n可能你會話用fb咪夠囉，但其實好多長輩都無社交軟件架<br />\n當佢地收到whatsapp呢類「流言」就會信到十足，先搞到咁多藍屍盲撐仆街保皇黨<br />\n<br />\n仲可以幫大家既藍色長輩改邪歸正！<br />\n文宣圖又有新既發放途徑！<br />\n<br />\n一齊集思廣益睇下有無效，亦都睇下有無人搞，大家覺得呢招WORK既就去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日林鄭打經濟牌玩民意睇到我好躁，大家仲有好多野可以做！唔好放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed71421632dc2d74e9cb3f997690f88f2dc3f36","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:07:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7c10213324c47a8c585b985606a7bf901cebbf3b","tid":1436546,"uid":4050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解一定係佢地開主題我地曬時間去駁佢？ 點解唔係我地開主題佢地之後回應我地</strong>？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想知<span style=\"color: green;\">鐳射筆，外國勢力，大台</span><br />\n<br />\n想知<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>葉虎，同志們，過期彈呀</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8b9c0421bc450e00fbe6693a0da6ca0d45a30002","tid":1436546,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:11:44.000Z","msg":"上呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a686b749360a63463fc98c86f83e31cd6573f71","tid":1436546,"uid":273619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:12:00.000Z","msg":"正，認同<br />\nwhatsapp可以普及到比更多人"},{"pid":"34bf52f2b898cd724a59a3c60f3ed89e3dc95d6b","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:14:26.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"868cb739d814c08c87ffe1c2a32f0da0a41a9dab","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:16:08.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"48311a84999f945d246281826547a3eb3c1d0dfa","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:16:44.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"e9ae17db201fc722131f86b3a53e86d16118bfe4","tid":1436546,"uid":229553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"9次"},{"pid":"a6d03ac1740ca8d17ed026bbb9916c1e4bc1f5be","tid